text: Lualua can refer to ==People== *Lomana LuaLua, a Zaire-born Congo DR international footballer who plays for Cypriot club Merit Alsancak Yeşilova *Kazenga LuaLua, younger brother of Lomana, plays for Luton Town ==Other== *Lualua (ship), also known as fou-lualua or foulua, a Samoan voyaging catamaran
title: LuaLua
